oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bob Jennings And The Farm Hands - WLAC - 1949-06-08
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: WLAC program featuring Bob Jennings and the Farm Hands, including Jerry Rivers (fiddle), Bill Martin (Bass), and Dwain Birdwell (steel guitar). Disc labeled as Wednesday June 8, year is likely 1949 based on performances, the presence of Jerry Rivers, and content on the other side of the disc.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Bob Jennings; Farm Hands
